<C>__{shaunessy's voice}
<D>__{ted? they've set the court date. i just heard today... it's...}
<P>__{(checking his notes)}
<D>__{january sixth.}
<C>__{ted}
<P>__{(despair)}
<D>__{oh, christ.. .john, there's some thing i ought to tell you. my... ah, situation has... changed. i lost my job.}
