<C>__{ted}
<D>__{john?}
<C>__{shaunessy's voice}
<P>__{(thoughtfully)}
<D>__{ted, i won't lie to you, we don't have a hope in hell of winning a custody hearing if you're out of work.}
<A>__{ted doubles over the phone like he has been hit in the stomach.}
